During a skype session on Friday, myself, Joel and Steve got some great files!  The strenght of the audio regarding our own Frank Sumption was truly amazing.  This is the best part of the communication and makes me proud to me apart of all of this.
   
  If its one thing for sure, they certainly love and know Frank!
   
  Enjoy!
  Juli
